	Unit Lens Books

This lens provides a unified search engine for books.
==================================================

I.    Description
II.   Requirements
III.  Compiling Library
IV.   Start Library
V.    Troubleshooting
VI.   Help, Feedback & Bug Reports
VII.  About


I.    Description
==================================================
This lens provides a unified search engine for
books. Currently the books muste be stored in
either ~/Documents or the Calibre database.

II.   Requirements
==================================================
Python, Unity, Calibre
Recommended: quickly

III.  Compiling Library
==================================================
sudo quickly install

IV.   Start Library
==================================================
quickly run

V.    Troubleshooting
==================================================
In need of help or for more information feel free
to send a mail to jnphilipp@gmail.com.

VI.   Help, Feedback & Bug Reports
==================================================
For Help, Feedback or Bug Reports, send a mail to
jnphilipp@gmail.com.


